Package itunesq

Class JSONHandler

java.lang.Object
itunesq.JSONHandler
public final class JSONHandler extends Object
Class that reads and processes the input JSON file.

This is a final class consisting entirely of static methods.

The main public method is processJSON, that uses a JSON reader to walk through the JSON file.
